items.title: +BMW Motorrad delivers first fleet of the electric scooter BMW C evolution to local police in Barcelona...

object.content:
+BMW Motorrad delivers first fleet of the electric scooter BMW C evolution to local police in Barcelona. http://press.bmwgroup.com/InjcK

A fleet of maxi scooters comprising 30 of the innovative BMW C evolution was delivered to the Barcelona City Hall for use by the local police. The first completely electrically powered scooter manufactured by BMW Motorrad will allow the police to move with maximum efficiency and zero emissions. #BMWMotorrad   #cevolution  ﻿
